OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStalker shot dead aimed    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcrossbow at police -       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwatchdog                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man armed with a crossbow, who was   
OL,6, shot dead by police after he broke into
OL,7, a home, had pointed the weapon at      
OL,8, officers, the police watchdog has said.
OL,10,FConvicted stalker Bryce Hodgson, from  
OL,11,FSheffield, was shot on 30 January in   
OL,12,FSurrey Quays, south-east London.       
OL,14,FThe 30-year-old had gained entrance to 
OL,15,Fthe property in Bywater Place armed    
OL,16,Fwith the crossbow and other weapons.   
OL,18,FHodgson had already swung a sword at   
OL,19,Fofficers, the Independent Office for   
OL,20,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) said.            
